# Paragraph Justification

This Project provides a Python program to justify text both left and right. It ensures no words are broken, fitting text within a specified page width.

## Files

- justify_text.py: Main script to justify text.
- test_justify_text.py: Unit tests for the text justification function.
- README: Project documentation.

## Usage

1. Execute the Python Program:

   python justify_paragraph_text.py

2. Test the python method "justify_paragraph" defined in "justify_text.py", using the python unit tests methods in "test_justify_text.py" file

   python -m unittest test_justify_text.py
